This is only needed if you use a Tablet / Touchscreen device.

Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\TabletPC
and change DWORD string
PreventHandwritingDataSharing
to
1


Finish.


For enterprise and education versions only: 
Go to
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SOFTWARE\Policies\Microsoft\Windows\CloudContent
and change DWORD string
DisableWindowsConsumerFeatures
to
1
